title: Coronavirus: Italy's Total Death Toll Exceeds 10,000
description: In the last 24 hours, 889 people have died in Italy from the Chinese coronavirus, bringing the nation's overall death toll from the virus to 10,023 as of Saturday — an increase of 9.7 percent in one day.
